{% set classPrefix = 'u-bolt-color-' %}
{% set utilityClasses = bolt.data.colors %}

<h4>Bolt Colors</h4>
<p>Add the utility class <code>.{{ classPrefix }}xx</code> where xx equals the text color you wish to apply.</p>

<div class="c-bolt-docs-color-demo">
  {% for key, collection in utilityClasses if key is not same as ('all') %}
    <div class="c-bolt-docs-color-demo__type">
      <h5>{{ key|capitalize }} Colors</h5>
      <div class="c-bolt-docs-color-demo__collection">
        {% for base, color in collection %}
          <div class="c-bolt-docs-color-demo__color">
            {% embed "@bolt/wrapper.twig" %}
              {% block wrapper_content %}
                {% grid with {
                  attributes: {
                  class: [
                    "o-bolt-grid--flex",
                    "o-bolt-grid--small",
                    "o-bolt-grid--matrix"
                  ]
                }
                  } %}
                  {% for variant in color|keys %}
                    {% if variant != 'base' %}
                      {% set tone = classPrefix ~ base ~ '-' ~ variant %}
                    {% else %}
                      {% set tone = classPrefix ~ base %}
                    {% endif %}
                    {% cell with {
                      attributes: {
                      class: [
                        "u-bolt-width-1/1",
                        color|length > 1 ? "u-bolt-width-1/2@small",
                        color|length > 2 ? "u-bolt-width-1/3@medium",
                        color|length > 3 ? "u-bolt-width-1/5@large"
                      ]
                    }
                      } %}
                      <div class="{{ tone }}">
                        <h6>{{ "#{base} #{variant}" | upper }}</h6>
                        <p><em>{{ '.' ~ tone }}</em></p>
                        <p>Ante justo sagittis fames facilisi sollicitudin tempor nunc parturient faucibus est amet
                          maecenas etiam fermentum eget, ullamcorper sociosqu suspendisse purus penatibus inceptos porta
                          adipiscing pharetra odio dis platea augue lobortis. Dui vitae erat posuere tempor ante nam
                          dictumst pretium felis accumsan mauris imperdiet eu, habitant taciti suspendisse vehicula
                          quisque curabitur velit parturient risus molestie consequat.</p>
                      </div>
                    {% endcell %}
                  {% endfor %}
                {% endgrid %}
              {% endblock %}
            {% endembed %}
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="c-bolt-docs-sassdoc-reference">
  <h5>SassDoc references</h5>
  <ul>
    <li><a target="_blank" href="{{ link['styleguide-sassdoc'] }}#function-bolt-color">@function bolt-color</a></li>
    <li><a target="_blank" href="{{ link['styleguide-sassdoc'] }}#mixin-bolt-color">@mixin bolt-color</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>